        public void update​(T row,
                   PartitionSpec spec,
                   StructLike partition)
        Description copied from interface: PositionDeltaWriter
        Inserts a new version of an existing row to the provided spec/partition.

        This method allows writers to distinguish new and updated records. The caller must separately invoke PositionDeltaWriter.delete(CharSequence, long, PartitionSpec, StructLike) for the original row position that is being updated.
